1. *Dosadna* mi je ova knjiga. (This book is *boring* to me.)
2. Ovaj film mi je *dosadio*. (I am *bored* with this movie.)
3. On je *dosadan* kad priča o svom poslu. (He is *tedious* when he talks about his job.)
4. Čekanje u redu je *dosadno*. (Waiting in line is *tedious*.)
5. *Dosadan* je život bez hobija. (Life without hobbies is *boring*.)
6. Nije mi *dosadno* kad sam sama. (I am not *bored* when I am alone.)
7. Moja sestra je *dosadna* kad se ljuti. (My sister is *irritating* when she is angry.)
8. *Dosadni* su mi ljudi koji stalno govore o sebi. (People who constantly talk about themselves are *annoying* to me.)
9. *Dosadno* je kada nemaš šta raditi. (It's *boring* when you have nothing to do.)
10. Posao je *dosadan*, ali bar dobro plaća. (The job is *tedious*, but at least it pays well.)